{title: Down In The Willow Garden}
{artist: The Osborne Brothers}
{composer: Written by Charlie Monroe}

[G]Down in the willow [Em]garden
My [G]love and I did [Em]meet
And [G]there we sat a court[Em]ing
My [G]love dropped [D7]off to [G]sleep
I [Em]had a bottle of [G]burgundy [Em]wine
My [G]young love did not [Em]know
